    <section type="chapter">
      <title>Momentum and impulse</title>
      <section type="section">
        <title>Introduction</title>
        <shortcode>ESBEO</shortcode>
        <para>In Grade 10 we studied motion but not what caused the motion. In this chapter we will learn that a net force is needed to cause motion. We recall what a force is and learn about how force and motion are related. We are introduced to two new concepts, momentum and impulse, and we learn more about turning forces and the force of gravity.</para>
